.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-IMBALANCE-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-imbalance-list \- FEAT-2145 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-imbalance-list
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2145).
.PP
Lists channels where local balance is below 30% or above 70% of total
capacity, indicating an imbalanced channel.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
